diablo2015

Class PhysicalConstants

  • java.lang.Object
    • diablo2015.PhysicalConstants

  • public class PhysicalConstants
extends java.lang.Object
    This class holds several constants that represent physical constants of the Robot. These can be PWM channels, Digital IO channels, dimensions, diametres, among other things.
    Author:
    Dylan Frese
